umber\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div><hr>\n<h2 id=\"_9-性能优化建议\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#_9-性能优化建议\"><span>9. 性能优化建议</span></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>预加载数据</strong>：在空闲时间预取可能用到的数据</li>\n<li><strong>缓存策略</strong>：对重复请求进行内存或本地存储缓存</li>\n<li><strong>请求合并</strong>：将多个小请求合并为一个批量请求</li>\n<li><strong>优先级调度</strong>：对关键任务设置更高的优先级</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"_10-总结\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#_10-总结\"><span>10. 总结</span></a></h2>\n<p>掌握多异步操作处理的关键在于：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>根据场景选择合适的 API（<code v-pre>all</code>/<code v-pre>race</code>/<code v-pre>any</code>）</li>\n<li>建立清晰的错误处理机制</li>\n<li>保持代码结构的简洁性</li>\n</ol>\n","env":{"base":"/","filePath":"G:/200-Project/hoey-blog-plume/docs/学文/25040101.md","filePathRelative":"学文/25040101.md","frontmatter":{"title":"如何优雅处理多个异步操作？","createTime":"2025/04/01 10:21:09","permalink":"/article/btjqqwlm/","tags":["JavaScript"]},"sfcBlocks":{"template":{"type":"template","content":"<template><p>在 JavaScript 开发中，经常会遇到需要处理多个异步操作的需要，为避免陷入回调地狱或逻辑混乱，总结了处理多异步任务的方法，包含 <code v-pre>Promise</code>、<code v-pre>async/await</code> 及常见陷阱解决方案。</p>\n<!-- more -->\n<h2 id=\"_1、传统异步问题-回调地狱\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#_1、传统异步问题-回调地狱\"><span>1、传统异步问题：回调地狱</span></a></h2>\n<div class=\"language-javascript line-numbers-mode\" data-highlighter=\"shiki\" data-ext=\"javascript\" style=\"--shiki-light:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee;--shiki-light-bg:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212\"><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\"\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">// 嵌套地狱示例</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">fetchUser</span><span style=\"--shiki-li